channel.title: Flog It!
channel.desc: The show comes from the RAF Museum at Hendon in London. Antiques experts Anita Manning and Mark Stacey find some real treasures among the bags and boxes to take to auction. There's a photo album of RAF Hendon in the 30s and a rare picture that brings a surprise in the saleroom, and Paul Martin visits an exhibition of First World War flying pioneers.
